name: Searching for a rental car with an age lesser than Twenty-one should display “Some car rental suppliers do not rent to young drivers. If you are travelling with an older person, it may help to makethem your main driver.”

steps.name: When  home page loaded click Car subtab in Book tab
Then  check Primary Driver is Twenty-one or older checkbox if it's unckecked
Then  fill out age input with less that Twenty-one
Then  fill out Going to and Dates and click Find cars button
And  verify that the new page has correct message
